---
title: Creamy Mushroom and Shrimp Alfredo with Linguine and Spinach
description: Perfect pasta doesn't take a lot of ingredients or time! This creamy shrimp Alfredo has a secret ingredient: soy sauce! Adding soy sauce to the mushrooms gives this Alfredo an umami kick.

